io.tarantool.driver.core

Interface TarantoolConnectionManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTarantoolConnectionManager, TarantoolClusterConnectionManager, TarantoolSingleConnectionManager

    public interface TarantoolConnectionManager
extends AutoCloseable
    Manages the Tarantool server connections lifecycle. Maintains multiple connections. Once a connection is lost, a connection procedure is performed.

    • Method Summary
